  <h1 class="d-flex justify-content-center">About this site</h1>
  <h4 class="d-flex text-center">This site is designed to allow users to sign-up, login, and post their
  own articles with titles and description text. There is also an admin functionality
  that allows admins to edit or delete any articles, or users that they wish to.
  This site should also appear and be functional on any number of devices, including
  mobile devices! If you see any overlapping or other odd behavior on your devices,
  please feel free to create an article about it, as we do not have email functionality
  built into the site just yet :)
<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
  **To get a profile picture, you would need to use Gravatar, which can be logged into using a WordPress account if you have one. This app searches Gravatar for your sign-up email, and if it matches your Gravatar/Wordpress, it will use your default picture! How cool is that?**
<br />
<br />
<br />
  **Admins and Owner can edit AND delete accounts/profiles**
  **Owner can do all functions**
  **Mods can edit other users' articles**
  **You can change your own username/password/email from your profile screen**
  **If you forget your password, an admin, or owner can set a new one for you, currently no email confirmation is needed, so there is no self-service "forgot password"!**
